data.description:
Hi all! Come support the Gamma Pledge Class of Beta Alpha Psi this week by buying some friendly, delectable DONUTS! 

Start your day off right and battle the cold weather by eating some sweet DONUTS and seeing our smiling faces :D Come visit! We’ll be selling them for 3 DAYS THIS WEEK (9AM-3PM) at $2 EACH or $3 FOR 2, don’t miss out! 

Locations:
Wednesday (2/20) - Langson and Gateway
Thursday (2/21) - Aldrich Plaza
Friday (2/22) - Aldrich Plaza

data.description:
Are in need of a study break? Are your hungry? Well come out and enjoy some wings at Buffalo Wild Wings to support Jodaiko! In doing so you support us for our spring concert, Henka.

Our fundraiser is from 9 pm to 1 am, right after Tomo No Kai's Day of Remembrance! Tomo No Kai's Day of Remembrance starts are 7:30 pm, It's free and I hear there are gonna be some awesome performances. If you guys can you guys should definitely go to that and then to our fundraiser!

Please make sure to bring a flyer that is in the post below. If not, we'll have a couple ready at the door when you arrive. We'd really appreciate your support! 

Thanks to Bryan Le for the event picture!
data.name: Jodaiko Buffalo Wild Wings Fundraiser!
